2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper also deals with ensuring security in addition to reliability, which is a key concern in cryptography and security. 
3. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper deals with a fading wiretap channel, which is a signal processing problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may be relevant to multimedia applications that require secure and reliable communication. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper may be relevant to networking applications that require secure and reliable communication.
